Everyone is pretending that nothing happened

598
00:40:17,639 --> 00:40:20,159
I know something's been drained from me

599
00:40:21,719 --> 00:40:23,400
But I can't tell what it is

600
00:40:30,639 --> 00:40:32,119
Call me when you get to the new school

601
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:27,880
When are you going to make trouble?

602
00:41:44,239 --> 00:41:45,880
Where is my passport?

603
00:41:46,719 --> 00:41:47,719
Stop asking

604
00:41:48,039 --> 00:41:49,239
You can't leave even if you have a passport.

605
00:41:51,039 --> 00:41:52,320
Please return your passport to me now

606
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:53,920
I just want to go back to see Yichen

607
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,320
you want to see him

608
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:57,519
Does he just want to see you?

609
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,480
Has he contacted you?

610
00:42:00,599 --> 00:42:02,039
Did he write you a letter back?

611
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:03,679
have you ever thought about

612
00:42:03,679 --> 00:42:05,840
He may have a new life of his own

613
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:08,159
Do you think everyone is as stupid as you?

614
00:42:09,639 --> 00:42:11,239
For a shady relationship

615
00:42:11,400 --> 00:42:13,079
Give up school, give up family

616
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:15,000
Give up everything you own

617
00:42:16,679 --> 00:42:18,159
Look at what you look like now

618
00:42:18,599 --> 00:42:19,840
Do you still have a personality?

619
00:43:03,639 --> 00:43:04,639
It's over in a while

620
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:05,920
Don't treat people to a drink

621
00:43:06,960 --> 00:43:08,039
He is still a child

622
00:43:08,039 --> 00:43:09,039
What to drink?

623
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:14,760
so long

624
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:16,159
No progress yet
